---
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative min-h-[90vh] md:min-h-screen flex items-center w-full pt-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden">
    <img 
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLuvzsXOWMtJ5nKK5X52hYtPuMaBqyAKhkh4UDN3byPEClkTnmL68M-RCY-AlGfqxmhQ2gWf_CMkCs0C2ydzzVWTVT39Lc8vSmlOxdMOdsUflUAZ_Gz0Jnn4LMsHP_ZiP6U2snibvPHsHrouYZD18e_8HpgmyLJ6fpDULOYUVCrnGxsRj7KNmBC0ayiHq2I8wdP2FvEZlXnldN2RZz1SILZxsUw6rmc6Mx0Cn-LN4_vCjCNWGovq2cwfL8M=w2560" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center filter brightness-[0.5] contrast-[1.2]" 
      id="hero-parallax-img" 
      alt="Hero background" 
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-track-asphalt/95 via-track-asphalt/70 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-track-asphalt via-track-asphalt/40 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 shimmer-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 px-gutter w-full max-w-container-max mx-auto flex flex-col items-start justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 border border-primary/30 bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-sm animate-fade-up">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[16px]">verified</span>
        <span class="font-label-caps text-microcopy text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">Acesso Restrito mediante seleção</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-hero-headline-mobile md:font-hero-headline text-hero-headline-mobile md:text-hero-headline text-performance-white mb-6 uppercase animate-fade-up delay-100">
        Onde o networking<br/><span class="text-primary">atinge 200km/h.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-metallic-grey mb-10 max-w-2xl animate-fade-up delay-200">
        Acelere conexões com os maiores tomadores de decisão do país em Interlagos. Uma experiência imersiva de pilotagem e negócios reservada para um grupo seleto de líderes executivos.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-up delay-300">
        <div class="inline-block p-4 -m-4 cursor-pointer" id="magnetic-wrapper">
          <a class="magnetic-btn justify-center items-center bg-podium-gold text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps px-8 py-4 uppercase tracking-widest transition-all duration-300 animate-breathe btn-glow" href="#aplicacao" id="magnetic-element" style="transform: translate(0px, 0px);">
            SOLICITAR ACESSO RESTRITO
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="inline-flex justify-center items-center border border-metallic-grey/40 text-performance-white font-label-caps text-label-caps px-8 py-4 uppercase tracking-widest hover:border-performance-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300 mt-0 sm:ml-4" href="#o-clube">
          CONHECER A PROPOSTA
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
